latestPosts.caption:
Overwhelmed, Overjoyed, Overblessed, Over-everything for this opportunity to host THE @priyankachopra for the launch of @maxfactor ‘s Full Bloom Colour Collection!! Priyanka is everything I aspire to be. Just sharing space with her and talk to her was a milestone I never thought I would achieve. This wouldn’t have been possible without your constant support so I am blessed to have a family like you guys 💕

I am my biggest critic and there have only been a few moments in my life where I have actually felt proud of myself. This was one of those moments. Goosebumps when I heard the news, goosebumps when I did it and I still get goosebumps that it happened. 

Truly blessed to have you all in my corner 🧿 Thank you!! And Thank you Maxfactor for this wonderful opportunity ✨

And a special thanks to my team at @iplixmedia without which none of this was possible!!💕

#priyankachopra #priyankachoprajonas #maxfactor
